Package: open-agenda
Architecture: all
Version: 1.1.0
Maintainer: Open-Agenda Team <team@open-agenda.org>
Depends: python3, python3-tk
Description: Open-Agenda v1.1 - The Ultimate Smart Calendar
 The best agenda in the world - Ultra modern 2025 interface!
 .
 Features:
  - Ultra modern 2025 dark interface with gradients
  - Auto-save - Your data is always saved!
  - Multiple calendars (personal, work, family, health)
  - Color categories for events
  - Priority levels (high, medium, low)
  - Light/Dark theme toggle
  - Search events
  - Export to JSON, CSV, ICS formats
  - Statistics dashboard
  - Keyboard shortcuts
  - Recurring events (daily, weekly, monthly, yearly)
  - Location and notes fields
  - Fully open source and free!
